    <title>M文件使用UTF-8编码</title>
    <link href="gulab.cn/2020/07/08/M%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8UTF8%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/"/>
    <id>gulab.cn/2020/07/08/M%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8UTF8%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/</id>
    <published>2020-07-08T11:19:19.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-07-08T11:57:11.527Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol type="1"><li>在MATLAB命令行窗口输入命令：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">feature(&#39;locale&#39;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>确认是否显示<code>jvmEncoding: 'UTF-8'</code>，如是，则现在已经是UTF-8编码；</p><a id="more"></a><ol start="2" type="1"><li>否则进入MATLAB的<code>bin</code>目录，复制<code>lcdata_utf8.xml</code>到桌面，并修改如下：</li></ol><ul><li>删除</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;encoding name&#x3D;”GBK”&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">  &lt; encoding_alias name&#x3D;”936”&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;encoding&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>修改</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;encoding name&#x3D;”UTF-8”&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">  &lt;encoding_alias name&#x3D;”utf8”&#x2F;&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;encoding&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>为</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;encoding name&#x3D;”UTF-8”&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">  &lt;encoding_alias name&#x3D;”utf8”&#x2F;&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">  &lt;encoding_alias name&#x3D;”GBK”&#x2F;&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;encoding&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3" type="1"><li><p>保存上述修改，文件重命名为<code>lcdata.xml</code>，复制（覆盖）到<code>bin</code>目录下；</p></li><li><p>重启MATLAB，检查并确认<code>jvmEncoding: 'UTF-8'</code>。</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;ol type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在MATLAB命令行窗口输入命令：&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;feature(&amp;#39;locale&amp;#39;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;确认是否显示&lt;code&gt;jvmEncoding: &#39;UTF-8&#39;&lt;/code&gt;，如是，则现在已经是UTF-8编码；&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
    
